1. stylesheet01.css
@media only screen (max-width:600px){
    .sidebar{
        display: none;
    }
    #test1{
        float: left;
    }
    #box{
        background-color: tomato;
    }
}

@media only screen (max-width:400px){
    #box{
        background-color: darkgreen;
    }
}
/* only screen: this @media effect can not be applied in PC browser, only applied in phone screen.*/

OR

@media  (min-width:400px) and (max-width:600px){
    .sidebar{
        display: none;
    }
    #test1{
        float: left;
    }
    #box{
        background-color: tomato;
    }
}
only between 400px and 600px width, this media queries will be applied

